      ],
      "orig": "A workstation able to run the diagnostic console is needed, along with the standard probe kit for this revision and a calibrated torque driver. A colour monitor is required so that the fault codes can be read during the bench checks. Use a grounded bench supply, and keep the capacitor discharge tool within reach before any panel on the chassis is opened for inspection.",
      "text": "A workstation able to run the diagnostic console is needed, along with the standard probe kit for this revision and a calibrated torque driver. A colour monitor is required so that the fault codes can be read during the bench checks. Use a grounded bench supply, and keep the capacitor discharge tool within reach before any panel on the chassis is opened for inspection."
    },
